C.Vox Full Sleeve Women's Quilted Jacket Price: Rs.2308

Understated colour comes with minimal details. This turtle neck sweatshirt will make a great wear for those chilly evenings. The zipper fly on the front can be zipped fully to carry that smart makeover. Layer it over a nice tee and a pair of slim fit jeans and shoes to match.
